# FlexServe AI Marketplace

FlexServe is an AI-powered service booking platform that connects customers with service providers through a centralized, secure, and easy-to-use marketplace. It aims to replace ad-hoc booking workflows (social media, chat, phone) with a reliable system that supports real-time availability, online payments, reviews, and AI-driven recommendations and fraud detection.

